[
    {
        "content": "<p>I'm struggling a bit with rewriting ovpn-dco in Rust - <a href=\"https://github.com/OpenVPN/ovpn-dco\">https://github.com/OpenVPN/ovpn-dco</a> Not sure what the best way to start is. As my very first steps I've been using the default template (rust-out-of-tree-module) where I'm trying to initialize the ovpn-dco module (basically trying to call exported C functions from my Rust code). Not sure what the best way is. As I said, I'd like to use the Rust module first to run the C code from it, but it never seems to compile properly (I guess I don't have enough knowledge in C). Should I be better off using bindings and the auto-generated ovpn_tcp_init? I've tried that before, but in both cases I get <code>undefined</code> which is related to that function. Please give me a hint and point me in the right direction - what would you do first if your goal was to rewrite this kernel module in Rust?</p>\n<p>Here is some code (I can provide all code if needed):</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://ovpn_dco_rust.rs\">ovpn_dco_rust.rs</a>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#![no_std]</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#![allow(improper_ctypes)]</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#![allow(warnings)]</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">prelude</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"p\">::{</span><span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">code</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">EINVAL</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">as</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">EinvalKern</span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n\n<span class=\"fm\">include!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"bindings.rs\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">module</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">type</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">OvpnDcoRust</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"ovpn_dco_rust\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">author</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"Vpnable Limited\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">description</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"OpenVPN data channel offload in Rust\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">license</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"GPL\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">OvpnDcoRust</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Module</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">OvpnDcoRust</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">init</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_module</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"nb\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">ThisModule</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">pr_info</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"ovpn_dco_rust module loaded.</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s\">\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ovpn_tcp_init</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">!=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">pr_err</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"ovpn_dco_rust: Failed to initialize TCP subsystem</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s\">\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">EinvalKern</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ovpn_netlink_register</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">!=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">pr_err</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"ovpn_dco_rust: Failed to register netlink</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s\">\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">EinvalKern</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">OvpnDcoRust</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Drop</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">OvpnDcoRust</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">drop</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">pr_info</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"ovpn_dco_rust module unloaded.</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s\">\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">ovpn_netlink_unregister</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"cp\">#[no_mangle]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">extern</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"C\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">ovpn_tcp_init</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">i32</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">ovpn_netlink_register</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">i32</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">ovpn_netlink_unregister</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Makefile:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Makefile\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c\"># SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0</span>\n<span class=\"c\"># Copyright (C) 2020- OpenVPN, Inc.</span>\n\n<span class=\"nv\">PWD</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">$(</span>shell<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">pwd</span><span class=\"k\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">KERNEL_SRC</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">?=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>/lib/modules/<span class=\"k\">$(</span>shell<span class=\"w\"> </span>uname<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r<span class=\"k\">)</span>/build\n\n<span class=\"cp\">ifeq ($(shell cd $(KERNEL_SRC) &amp;&amp; pwd),)</span>\n<span class=\"k\">$(</span><span class=\"nv\">warning</span> <span class=\"k\">$(</span><span class=\"nv\">KERNEL_SRC</span><span class=\"k\">)</span> <span class=\"nv\">is</span> <span class=\"nv\">missing</span>, <span class=\"nv\">please</span> <span class=\"nv\">set</span> <span class=\"nv\">KERNEL_SRC</span><span class=\"k\">)</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">endif</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">export</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">KERNEL_SRC</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">RM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">?=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>rm<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f\n<span class=\"nv\">DEPMOD</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>depmod<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a\n\n<span class=\"nv\">REVISION</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">$(</span>shell<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"k\">$(</span>PWD<span class=\"k\">)</span><span class=\"s2\">/.git\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">then</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nb\">echo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">$$</span><span class=\"o\">(</span>git<span class=\"w\"> </span>--git-dir<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"k\">$(</span>PWD<span class=\"k\">)</span><span class=\"s2\">/.git\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>describe<span class=\"